data.description: This gorgeous 3 bedrooms, 2-1/2 baths and 2 car garage includes a spacious great room LOCATED AT STONEYBROOK OF VENICE . YOU WILL LOVE THE FENCED IN YARD AND THE HUGE LAKE VIEW. The bonus/flex area upstairs can be utilized as a den or as a playroom or an office. The master bath has dual sinks and a tub as well as a separate shower which is great and the two other bedrooms are a good size. The whole house is light and bright and there is NO Carpeting. At Stoneybrook of Venice the recreational facility is state of the art with a resort style pool and a spa and an area for the children or grandchildren to splash around. There is also a media room which you can reserve to have a movie showing and an internet lounge as well as many other areas including a huge fitness center. Save money on the gym! Inline skating, a baseball diamond, a playground and tennis courts. In Stoneybrook you are as busy as you want to be with the full time social director giving a helping hand. Come and see this lovely property. You will be glad you did. It is a straight run down Center Road to Venice Island and the BEACH.
